  "texts": [
    "Figure 1b presents a schematic that highlights the measurement levels, the reference axes, and the locations that contain the damage mechanisms.",
    "Figure 1c shows the damage mechanisms that are installed on the lowest damage level of the structure.",
    "An in-depth discussion of the damage states is held in Section 3.1.",
    "As the structure is situated outside, it is excited by natural sources.",
    "As a result, the structure represents a realistic case for SHM monitoring."
